column5: Open water on BOQ is slowly coming to the end
Awww....I was hoping to see some monster eyes in this post....sniff sniff....this is depressing...
I would not say that as of yet, the weather is warm right now and all of our snow is practically gone.  Still good for eyes presently until it begins to feeze.  Regards, Sam
Thanks for the update folks... I'm very much interested in any and all reports regarding the status of the Q and it's availabilty for fishing opportunities! Please, keep them coming! HH
